{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"code":"environmentAncestor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"code":"environmentDescendant","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"code":"apply(context:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"code":"UIView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" conformers "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must"}]},{"type":"text","text":" call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}]}],"type":"aside","style":"important","name":"Important"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/uikit\/uiview\/environment"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0